00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:37,634
Yeah, 'cause you acted all cool
and everything with Wilson,

371
00:19:37,718 --> 00:19:41,012
but you feel comfortable enough
with me that you can freak out.

372
00:19:41,097 --> 00:19:42,389
That's cool.

373
00:19:49,272 --> 00:19:53,275
His sinuses are clear. The
antibiotics should work this time.

374
00:19:54,861 --> 00:19:56,862
Why did you forgive me?

375
00:19:57,405 --> 00:20:01,408
I mean, I'm glad, I'm
grateful, but I'm confused.

376
00:20:01,492 --> 00:20:03,733
You've been harder on the
patient than you've been on me.

377
00:20:03,786 --> 00:20:09,583
The difference between you and the
patient is that you feel shame, guilt.

378
00:20:10,835 --> 00:20:13,920
That's how I know we're
gonna get through this.

379
00:20:16,173 --> 00:20:17,674
My stomach.

380
